msgstr "Laman tidak ditemukan"

#: 404.php:5
msgid ""
"We're sorry, the page or file you requested was not found on this server."
msgstr ""
"Maaf, halaman atau berkas yang Anda inginkan tidak dapat ditemukan di server"
" ini."

#: 404.php:7
msgid ""
"If you clicked on a link that brought you to this page, or you have reached "
"this page through a search engine or bookmark, it could very well be that "
"the page you were looking for was removed, renamed or temporary unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda membuka sebuah tautan yang membawa Anda ke halaman ini, atau Anda "
"mencapai halaman ini melalui mesin pencari atau markah buku, hampir "
"dipastikan halaman yang Anda cari telah dihapus, berganti nama atau untuk "
"sementara tidak tersedia."

#: 404.php:10
msgid ""
"Please try one of the following methods to find the page you are looking "
"for:"
msgstr ""
"Silakan coba salah satu metode berikut untuk menemukan halaman yang Anda "
"cari:"

#: 404.php:14
msgid ""
"If you typed the page address in the Address bar, make sure that it is "
"spelled correctly."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda mengetik alamat halaman di batang Alamat, pastikan ejaannya telah "
"benar."

#: 404.php:16
msgid "Click the Back button to try another link."
msgstr "Klik tombol Kembali untuk mencoba tautan lain."

