#: frontpage.php:20
msgid ""
"The default Xfce Desktop provides a simple and attractive desktop for Unix "
"users."
msgstr ""
"Desktop Xfce standar menyediakan desktop yang sederhana dan menarik bagi "
"pengguna Unix."

#: frontpage.php:25
msgid ""
"The Xfce Desktop provides all the required settings to configure your "
"hardware, desktop appearance and other desktop-critical settings allowing "
"you to easily manage your system."
msgstr ""
"Desktop Xfce menyediakan semua pengaturan yang diperlukan untuk mengatur "
"peranti keras Anda, tampilan desktop dan pengaturan pentng-desktop yang "
"memungkinkan Anda untuk dengan mudah mengelola sistem Anda."

#: frontpage.php:26
msgid ""
"The Xfce Window Manager is the core of the desktop. It can be tuned to make "
"window management quick and predictable. It also features around 100 border "
"styles giving it the look you want!"
msgstr ""
"Manajer Jendela Xfce adalah inti dari desktop. Ia dapat diatur untuk membuat"
" manajemen jendela cepat dan mudah diprediksi. Ia juga mempunyai fitur "
"sekitar 100 gaya batas yang memberikan tampilan seperti yang Anda inginkan!"

#: frontpage.php:27
msgid ""
"The Xfce Panel can be customized in numerous ways so it provides all the "
"items you need right where you need them. It has three different display "
"modes, transparency and a few dozen different plugins."
msgstr ""
"Panel Xfce dapat disesuaikan dalam beragam cara sehingga memberikan semua "
"item yang Anda perlukan kapanpun Anda butuhkan. Ia mempunyai tiga mode "
"tampilan yang berbeda, transparansi dan beberapa lusin plugin yang berbeda."

#: frontpage.php:30
msgid ""
"Beside the core desktop functionality, a number of other applications are "
"developed in the Xfce repositories, like an image viewer, task manager, "
"notes plugin and calendar."
msgstr ""
"Selain fungsionalitas desktop inti, sejumlah aplikasi lain dikembangkan di "
"repositori Xfce, seperti penampil gambar, manajer tugas, plugin catatan, dan"
" kalender."

